{"tid":959029,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國加州警員疑被偷渡者槍殺　特朗普稱是時候建圍牆","createTime":"2018-12-28T09:26:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-28T10:23:47.000Z","uid":39464,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"edb2e05cb60fa0a255d74e2cbd1df50006c18278","tid":959029,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T09:26:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1435420_1_20181228155742.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1435420_1_20181228155742.jpg&h=ca0af47f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國加州一名警員，懷疑被非法入境者槍殺，警方正全力追捕疑兇。總統特朗普在社交專頁提到案件時說，是時候興建邊境圍牆，加強邊境保安。<br />\n<br />\n案發在加州北部小鎮紐曼，33歲警員辛格在當地星期三凌晨一時左右，截查一架汽車時，與懷疑酒後駕駛的司機駁火。司機其後逃去，辛格身中幾槍，送院搶救後不治。<br />\n<br />\n警方說經調查後，懷疑涉案司機非法進入並居留在美國，手上有武器，是危險人物。警方又說辛格是斐濟人，其後移民到美國，成為一名警察。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1435420-20181228.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1435420-20181228.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=HyHbeLBSYBMh6yY%2BD52dr5zN29kXmk9bB7xBuKM86BA%3D&h=1a8414a7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1435420-20181228.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=f7dcbb3c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1435420-20181228.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"5323a074344b1bd61269f6ab2e14811199dbcca7","tid":959029,"uid":34410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T09:30:07.000Z","msg":"左膠:一日最衰都係NRA同侵侵,難民是無辜的"},{"pid":"39575cc0160936a9ec319e86143fdcee0040e08e","tid":959029,"uid":51057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T09:33:56.000Z","msg":"對住個醉酒佬, 又唔係比人偷襲, 咁都輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw rip<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be4686eab086c57e98e0b7f586b9fc8d316